<Could you fab a liner out of steel then place that in a plastic container?>

Great Idea! Get one of those plastic barrels (the BIG ones) and then cut a piece of expanded steel (steel grating used in the bottom of trailers these days around here). Wrap it around the inside of the barrel making a tube basically. Presto. No rusty barrel. 

